me":"2018-12-06T12:48:33.000Z","msg":"其實陳雲講ge野係抄客家人,一d都唔係新野!!!!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/103243\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/103243</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6711e77988fb6270d6cefd292ef2cd16f98aed32","tid":930525,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T12:50:36.000Z","msg":"客家話極速收皮係奶共惡果！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/369982\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/369982</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b96cc0ca38fc39136bafbdd81f2511092a8376f3","tid":930525,"uid":53705,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T12:51:45.000Z","msg":"標題應該改一改<br />\n<br />\n為什麼有人說<del>潮州人</del> 中國人 很討厭呢？"},{"pid":"9223dc263eb5a2e67b98fb8150bda699ede7b945","tid":930525,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T12:59:02.000Z","msg":"「家己郞」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"469f55b61c3cda6d3f575db3d61d6d366486f880","tid":930525,"uid":215603,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"948863669901bf1f135fe1f18491cf0653de4438","tid":930525,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T12:36:01.000Z","msg":"講仆街客家人先最仆街，有無聽過客家佔地主？？仆街客家人最佳例子&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;陳云根"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T13:14:51.000Z","msg":"和勝和變成以客家人與圍頭人（佘佬）為主要成員，故1980前也被俗稱為佘幫或客家幫。香港原居民中的五大氏族：鄧族、廖族、文族、侯族、彭族與和勝和138年來乃是一體化關係。"},{"pid":"696f68614e4161ee95279f78b384fdd8ac16c5f2","tid":930525,"uid":215603,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T13:36:26.000Z","msg":"一个潮汕人眼中的潮汕人十大劣根 <br />\n<br />\n1.排外 <br />\n2.跟风 <br />\n3.窝里斗 <br />\n4.发财不问来路 <br />\n5.宗族门派观念 <br />\n6.封建迷信 <br />\n7.不重视教育 <br />\n8.重男轻女 <br />\n9.官本位 <br />\n10.走后门 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.douban.com/group/topic/2292776/\" data